cat > wkgtk-html2pdf.1 <<EOF
.TH WKGTK-HTML2PDF 1 "February 2026" "0.0.16" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
wkgtk-html2pdf \- modern WebKit-based HTML to PDF converter
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B wkgtk-html2pdf
[\fIOPTIONS\fR] \fB\-i\fR \fIinput.html\fR \fB\-o\fR \fIoutput.pdf\fR
.SH DESCRIPTION
.B wkgtk-html2pdf
is a powerful tool for converting HTML content into high-quality PDF documents 
using WebKitGTK. Developed as a modern alternative to the archived \fBwkhtmltopdf\fR, 
it provides a clean interface for embedding in applications and a 
simple command-line interface for quick conversions.
.PP
The tool supports advanced features such as internal anchors, links, and nested 
sidebar indexing. It includes built-in CSS templates for all standard ISO and 
US paper sizes to prevent extraneous blank pages and maintain layout consistency.
.SH DOCUMENTATION
This manual is derived from the official project documentation. 
While this man page provides a standard system reference, the 
full HTML version of this manual is a self-fulfilling prophecy: 
it is generated entirely using \fBwkgtk-html2pdf\fR to 
demonstrate the tool's professional typesetting and 
indexing capabilities.
.SH OPTIONS
.TP
.BR \-h ", " \-\-help
Display the help message and exit.
.TP
.BR \-v ", " \-\-verbose " \fILEVEL\fR"
Set the log level (1-7). Logs are written to the system journal.
.TP
.BR \-i ", " \-\-infile " \fIFILE\fR"
Specify the source HTML file to convert.
.TP
.BR \-o ", " \-\-outfile " \fIFILE\fR"
Specify the output PDF file name.
.TP
.BR \-O ", " \-\-orientation " \fI[portrait|landscape]\fR"
Set page orientation (Default: portrait).
.TP
.BR \-s ", " \-\-size " \fISIZE\fR"
Set the page size (Default: A4).
.TP
.BR \-r ", " \-\-relative-uri
Look for assets (images, CSS) in the current folder relative to the input file.
.SH SEE ALSO
.BR xvfb (1)
EOF

